      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like i'm waiting for something that's never coming back. every day is just more of the same... waking up, eating, staring at his chair, and going back to sleep. it's so exhausting. it feels like the version of me that was actually alive died with him. i'm just going through the motions of a life that doesn't even make sense anymore.",
