      "content": "the \"spark\" feels so a long way off. like, what's the point of waiting for a spark in a house that's just dead? there's no color left in anything. i look at the future and i just see... nothing. just more of this grey, endless nothing. it feels less like i'm living and more like i'm just waiting to be done.",
